	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_SMR_smr_loot_repair_parts_spawn_desc">
		<text>Enables/disables part repair items as minor repair kits. If you don't want to bother with repairing/replacing weapon and outfit parts, you can disable spawns for related items.</text>
	</string>
